tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  24,7,"Refti e nder seedagol makko jowaɓol ngol o ɓeyda huɗirgol wonkii makko jojjidugol e kuddi ndin si o laatike fenuɗu e ko o tukkire kon [sonnaajo on]."
  24,9,"Refti e nder seedagol makko jowaɓol ngol o ɓeyda huɗirgol wonkii makko kin tikkere Alla nden e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike goonguɗo e nder ko o tukkiri mo kon."